1
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,200
My Lord.

2
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,120
It is that room.

3
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:00,200
Has he been alerted?

4
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:00,680
Not yet.

5
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,320
I saw Liu Mu go in with my own eyes.

6
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:02,800
Arrest him.

7
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:03,320
Yes, sir.

8
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,240
What a slippery old eel.

9
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:23,640
After him!

10
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:24,080
No need.

11
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,960
I know where he is going.

12
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:31,000
I want Great Fortune.

13
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,920
I want Great Fortune.

14
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,200
I want a swift rise to power.

15
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,920
I want a swift rise to power.

16
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,960
Boundless greed.

17
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,560
A beast in human skin.

18
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,200
Return to Dali Temple with me.

19
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:51,760
I want Great Fortune.

20
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:52,760
I want Great Fortune.

21
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:53,640
I want Great Fortune.

22
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,520
Liu Mu.

23
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,280
Move out of the way.

24
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,800
He must die today.

25
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,120
I want Great Fortune.

26
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,880
The Tang Code will punish him.

27
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:18,960
I want Great Fortune.

28
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,720
When he murdered my little brother...

29
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,080
...where was the Tang Code?

30
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,120
The Tang Code...

31
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,080
I want Great Fortune.

32
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,000
...was made only for you aristocrats.

33
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,240
If you do not move aside today...

34
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,760
...I will kill you too.

35
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,520
Die!

36
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,040
Liu Mu, stop!

37
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,200
Liu Mu!

38
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,520
If I am not mistaken...

39
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,360
...was your family member also...

40
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:21,440
I want Great Fortune.

41
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,720
I want a swift rise to power.

42
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,360
A swift rise to power.

43
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,600
I want Great Fortune.

44
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,600
Great Fortune.

45
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:28,320
Come.

46
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,920
If you like it, Little Brother...

47
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,160
...Big Brother will buy you more later.

48
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,040
Okay.

49
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:38,600
Madam.

50
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:39,360
Madam.

51
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:39,960
Please, sit down.

52
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:40,560
Here.

53
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,480
Madam, are you alright?

54
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:44,640
Young Master.

55
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:45,960
My stomach hurts.

56
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,800
Could you fetch me some medicine?

57
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,200
But I...

58
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,400
I will watch the child for you.

59
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:54,960
Don't worry.

60
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,040
I am not a bad person.

61
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,040
Young Master.

62
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:58,920
Hurry.

63
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,160
Little Brother.

64
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,880
Wait here for Big Brother like a good boy.

65
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,040
Don't run off, understand?

66
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:06,520
Mm-hmm.

67
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,120
Big Brother will be right back.

68
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:08,800
Okay?

69
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,440
Wait here for Big Brother.

70
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,280
Just wait right here for Big Brother.

71
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,080
Here.

72
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:20,640
Madam, the medicine.

73
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:28,800
Little Brother!

74
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,120
My little brother...

75
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,480
...was murdered by him just like that.

76
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,320
I want Great Fortune.

77
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,800
I saved someone out of kindness...

78
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,200
...but met a villain instead.

79
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,480
I searched for days...

80
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,400
...but found no trace of my little brother.

81
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,600
By chance, I discovered...

82
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,640
...that woman was actually Li Niangu's concubine.

83
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,720
I want a swift rise to power.

84
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:56,840
Then why not report it to the authorities?

85
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,320
Report it?

86
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,480
He is an official!

87
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,360
Could I possibly win against him?

88
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,000
Most likely...

89
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,680
...I wouldn't even make it out of the government office doors.

90
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,680
I had no choice but to take revenge myself.

91
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,440
You found out...

92
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,160
...that Madam Zhang likes Huaiyang Cuisine...

93
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,280
...so you mastered a craft in a very short time.

94
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,280
You infiltrated the Li Manor

95
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,200
Aren't you afraid Hong Xiu will discover you?

96
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,440
That woman...

97
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,400
is pampered and spoiled.

98
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,880
Our kitchen is so dirty,

99
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,280
why would she ever come here?

100
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,600
I couldn't see her even if I wanted to.

101
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:45,280
Even though I've stayed in this Li Manor for half a year,

102
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,240
I still can't find any trace of my little brother.

103
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,960
Until recently.

104
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,240
Master

105
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,200
The soup is ready.

106
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:55,920
Mm.

107
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,400
You may leave.

108
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:01,360
Yes.

109
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,280
Divine Master.

110
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,480
Why is it that the boy used for the Foundation Sacrifice

111
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,080
has been buried for over half a year,

112
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,760
yet my career fortune is still poor?

113
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,320
I've only been promoted a tiny bit!

114
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,400
Rest assured, My Lord.

115
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,800
I have found a pair for a Dragon-Phoenix Foundation Sacrifice for you.

116
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,040
One buried in the front yard,

117
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,360
one placed behind the house.

118
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,320
They will ensure your safety and success.

119
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:23,880
Oh?

120
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,640
Where did you find

121
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,800
this dragon and phoenix pair?

122
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,880
Right here in your manor, My Lord.

123
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,240
Good, good.

124
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,080
You dug up Hong Xiu's stillborn fetus and severed its head

125
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,960
to intimidate Madam Zhang?

126
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,080
Yes.

127
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,480
Then why did you kill Madam Zhang?

128
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,240
That goddamn Divine Master...

129
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,880
it was Madam Zhang who introduced him to that thief.

130
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,240
Great Fortune, Great Fortune, Great Fortune.

131
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,120
I want Great Fortune.

132
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,320
But she didn't know she was inviting a wolf into the house.

133
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,880
The Divine Master and Hong Xiu were already having an affair.

134
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,960
All for Li Niangu's family fortune.

135
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,160
He is even more pitiful.

136
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:05,040
He might never know in his life

137
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,800
that the dead child belonged to the Divine Master.

138
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,440
Retribution.

139
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,080
It's retribution.

140
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,000
In that case,

141
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,160
you must also know

142
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,400
who caused Hong Xiu's fetus to die in the womb.

143
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,200
Of course.

144
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,360
You vixen!

145
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,760
It's one thing to seduce my husband,

146
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,360
but I haven't even conceived yet,

147
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,960
and you've gone and gotten pregnant first!

148
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:37,760
However,

149
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:41,600
I don't think you'll have the luck to give birth to it.

150
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:46,760
Give me Great Fortune!

151
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,840
I want Great Fortune!

152
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,480
I want a swift rise to power!

153
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,120
Dig it open.

154
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,320
Lay it down.

155
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,160
I want Great Fortune.

156
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,880
I want Great Fortune.

157
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,280
My Lord,

158
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,480
the one behind the house has been dug up too.

159
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,480
I want a swift rise to power.

160
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,040
Open the coffin.

161
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,440
Brother!

162
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,880
Brother!

163
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,320
I want Great Fortune.

164
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,000
Brother!

165
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,120
Acting Vice Minister,

166
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,680
regarding this case,

167
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,080
how shall we judge?

168
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:54,920
Li Niangu.

169
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:55,920
Cruel and inhumane.

170
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,120
Disregarding human relations.

171
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,960
Committing acts that outrage both gods and men.

172
00:08:59,600 --> 00:08:59,960
Behead him.

173
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,320
I want Great Fortune.
